.TH ORDEROFTWILIGHT 6 "November 2025"
.SH NAME
orderoftwilight \- Puzzle platformer with muscle memory.

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B orderoftwilight

.SH DESCRIPTION
The game is about Twilight Sparkle's mind being in chaos, and going through
levels to find what is truly important to her.
.PP
This is a game where you use your arrow keys to cast a number of different
spells to help you progress through the levels. It has a dozen levels to go
through and a challenge mode to test your wits.
.PP
\fBorderoftwilight\fP is a graphical action platform game built using Lua and
the LOVE framework. This command executes a bash script
of the orderoftwilight.love package against the love executable.

.SH OPTIONS
None.

